{"title":"炊烟（外一首）","authors":["刘昌庆"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":2,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘昌庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是植于家园中的一种高秆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比红高粱金谷子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高出许多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟拔节的时候便吐出一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穗穗籽粒饱满的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情  让人想到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被灶火映红脸庞的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到用草绳搓长日子的父"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到一种野菜的味道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我挂在祖母唇边的乳名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暮归的风里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅袅炊烟飘得很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子也飘得很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛炊烟是日子的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为五谷之魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟常弥漫于我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分行文字中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一读  便呛出满眼眶的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡思之泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在故乡  民俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往往与五谷间作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它与红高粱金谷子一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葱茏着这片古老的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着篱笆  伸手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓住那些无形的叶子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便可顺藤摸到民俗的根部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜活的根  一直扎在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间深处或冷暖民间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在故乡  月饼粽子茱萸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯笼对联门神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是民俗的几种比喻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它原汁原味的词义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一些阳光和雨露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着我们的骨骼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点一点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔节为龙的脊柱"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}